      <section>
         <p>The setup of the system cooling system depends on different
factors. Generally, one power module (<ph otherprops="IEC">20 kVA</ph>
            <ph otherprops="UL">12.5 kVA</ph>) is equipped with tree fans (E101).</p>
         <p>If the system is configured with input and output
transformers, additional cooling fans are mounted for transformer
cooling (E701).</p>
         <p>Only for 75-100 kVA UPS: If
the system is configured with input and bypass transformers, additional
cooling fans are mounted for transformer cooling (E701).</p>
         <p>The
static bypass switch module is also equipped with three fans (E401). </p>
         <p>
            <ph>Only for 25-50 kVA UPS: </ph>To increase the air circulation
in the cabinet, one additional fan is mounted in the static bypass
switch module.</p>
         <p>All fan modules are equipped with similar speed
monitoring boards.</p>
      </section>
